        <section id="parks">
            <h2>Top 3 Must-Visit Parks</h2>
            <article>
                <h3>1. Yosemite National Park</h3>
                <img src="yosemite-valley.jpg" 
                     alt="Yosemite Valley with El Capitan rock formation and waterfall" 
                     width="600" height="400">
                <p>Famous for its waterfalls, deep valleys, and ancient sequoias.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Location: California</li>
                    <li>Established: 1890</li>
                    <li>Best feature: Half Dome</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article>
                <h3>2. Grand Canyon National Park</h3>
                <img src="grand-canyon.jpg" 
                     alt="Panoramic view of Grand Canyon's layered red rock formations" 
                     width="600" height="400">
                <p>Home to one of the world's most spectacular geological wonders.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Location: Arizona</li>
                    <li>Established: 1919</li>
                    <li>Best feature: South Rim views</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article>
                <h3>3. Acadia National Park</h3>
                <img src="acadia-park.jpg" 
                     alt="Ocean meeting rocky coastline at Acadia National Park at sunrise" 
                     width="600" height="400">
                <p>Where mountains meet the Atlantic Ocean along Maine's coast.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Location: Maine</li>
                    <li>Established: 1919</li>
                    <li>Best feature: Cadillac Mountain sunrise</li>
                </ul>
            </article>
        </section>

        <section id="tips">
            <h2>Essential Travel Tips</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Check park websites for alerts and closures</li>
                <li>Arrive early to avoid crowds</li>
                <li>Pack layers - mountain weather changes quickly</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

